      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of clinically relevant loading rates and environmental conditions, or deviations are justified.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single crosshead displacement rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717 protocol. No alternative loading rates or temperature conditions were evaluated. This represents a single test condition, falling below the required level. The deviation is noted as a limitation; the quasi-static rate is considered representative of the worst-case clinical scenario for static overload."
    },
