      "rationale": "E/uval values of 1.41, 1.62, and 1.83 were computed for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement respectively, all below the 1.96 threshold. Force-displacement curves from all 11 constructs were overlaid with the FEA prediction band; the model trace lies within the experimental corridor across the full displacement range."
